---
source: memory-cli/tests/snapshot_tests.rs
expression: stdout
---
Tag management commands for episodes

Usage: memory-cli tag <COMMAND>

Commands:
  add     Add tags to an episode
  remove  Remove tags from an episode
  set     Set/replace all tags on an episode
  list    List tags - optionally for a specific episode or all tags system-wide
  search  Search episodes by tags
  show    Show episode details with its tags
  rename  Rename a tag across all episodes
  stats   Show detailed tag usage statistics
  help    Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help
